<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulrich Amman zu Kelheim</head><p>Der Rat teilt Unkenntnis vom Verbleib von Ammans Knecht mit und verspricht Erkundigung nach namentlicher Nennung eines Bürgers zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_77" id="38r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_77_r3l22"><expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Amman geſeʒʒen cʒü Kelheim / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_77_r3l23"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> knechts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r3l24"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> /. Davon wıſſen wır cʒü der cʒeit nichts / So habt Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r3l25">auch keinen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> benant /. Dann weſt Jr dheinen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r3l26"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / der ew ıhts beſchuldıgt / wenn Jr vns den <expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan> benennet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r3l27">So wöllen wir ſein rede hören / vnd ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r3l28">laſſen wıſſen / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_77" id="38r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Amman, gesezzen czü Kelheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                                  <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> und
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> knechts
                                                  <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, davon wissen wir
                                                czü der czeit nichts. So habt ir uns auch keinen
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> benant. Dann west ir
                                                dheinen <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, der ew ihts
                                                beschuldigt, wenn ir uns den <expan>mit
                                                  name<ex>n</ex></expan> benennet, so wöllen wir
                                                sein rede hören und ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein
                                                  <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> lassen wissen.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
